  "title": "Accounting Internship",
  "description": "<p>Company Profile</p>\n<p>lichen holding singapore pte ltd  is a subsidary of lichen global ,a NASDA listed company in managemnt  consultancy ,listing FA services. We are a team with 10 years of experiences in accounting (in-house and outsource account support) , corporate secretarial services , company formation, taxation ( corporate tax, personal tax and GST) , human resource and payroll support , customized training course, internal control in operation and finance areas and supply chain management.</p>\n<p>Our clients ranges from SME startups to MNCs, across all industries.</p>\n<p>Job Description</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>General Ledger Maintenance: Support the maintenance of accurate ledgers and records, ensuring compliance with accounting principles.</li>\n  <li>Account Reconciliation: Perform reconciliations of bank statements and accounts payable/receivable.</li>\n  <li>Data Entry: Accurately enter financial transactions into accounting software and maintain organized records.</li>\n  <li>Tax Filings: Aid in the preparation of tax documents and filings, ensuring adherence to relevant regulations.</li>\n  <li>Administrative Support: Provide general administrative support to the accounting department, including scheduling meetings and managing documentation.</li>\n  <li>Special Projects: Participate in special projects and initiatives as assigned by the accounting team.</li>\n</ul>",
